<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FF0192C6FE50FA76" bold="true" box="[160,480,1494,1520]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Justification of the transfer</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF236D344052323FF0192EAFC32FF6B" blockId="16.[160,1156,1494,1728]" lastBlockId="17.[160,1155,142,271]" lastPageId="17" lastPageNumber="2855" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244052322FF0192EAFE94F995" author="Patel SK" box="[160,292,1530,1555]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="44 - 46" refId="ref7664" refString="Patel SK. 1988. A new species of spider of the genus: Sergiolus (Gnaphosidae) from India. Biol Bull India. 10: 44 - 46." type="journal article" year="1988">Patel (1988)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044052322FE3F92EAFD94F995" authorityName="Patel" authorityYear="1988" box="[414,548,1530,1555]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiarae">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FE3F92EAFD94F995" box="[414,548,1530,1555]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">S. khodiarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on a 
<typeStatus id="54F6887144052322FD0A92EAFCBFF995" box="[683,783,1530,1555]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">holotype</typeStatus>
female collected in 
<collectingRegion id="4989F83144052322FC4E92EAFBF3F995" box="[1007,1091,1530,1555]" country="India" name="Gujarat" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Gujarat</collectingRegion>
. Even though we were unable to examine the type specimen of this species, which is presumably lost, the original illustrations of the epigyne of this species show that it lacks diagnostic features of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044052322FE389172FE4AF9FD" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1892" box="[409,506,1634,1659]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FE389172FE4AF9FD" box="[409,506,1634,1659]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Sergiolus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(see previous paragraph on 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044052322FC9B9172FBA8F9FD" authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" baseAuthorityYear="2021" box="[826,1048,1634,1659]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lamhetaghatensis">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FC9B9172FBA8F9FD" box="[826,1048,1634,1659]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">H. lamhetaghatensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
); instead, it resembles the species of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044052322FE7E9195FCAEF918" authority="Westring, 1874" authorityName="Westring" authorityYear="1874" box="[479,798,1669,1694]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FE7E9195FDDAF918" box="[479,618,1669,1694]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">Poecilochroa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244052322FDD59195FCAEF918" author="Westring N" box="[628,798,1669,1694]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="1 - 68" refId="ref8151" refString="Westring N. 1874. Bemerkungen uber die Arachnologischen Abhandlungen von Dr T. Thorell unter dem Titel: 1 °, On European Spiders, pts 1 et 2, Upsala, 1869 - 70. 2 °, Remarks on Synonyms of European Spiders, Upsala, 1872 - 73. Goteborgs Kungliga Vetenskaps och Vitterhets Samhalles Handlingar 14: 1 - 68." type="journal article" year="1874">Westring, 1874</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
as illustrated for 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044052322FC4D9195FEF4F946" authority="(Tikader, 1982)" baseAuthorityName="Tikader" baseAuthorityYear="1982" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="poonaensis">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FC4D9195FB33F918" box="[1004,1155,1669,1694]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">P. poonaensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244052322FF0791B7FE8DF946" author="Tikader BK" box="[166,317,1703,1728]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="295 - 536" refId="ref8093" refString="Tikader BK. 1982. Family Gnaphosidae. Fauna India (Araneae). 3: 295 - 536." type="journal article" year="1982">Tikader, 1982</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044052322FEDD91B7FD30F946" authority="Paik, 1992" authorityName="Paik" authorityYear="1992" box="[380,640,1703,1728]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="taeguensis">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144052322FEDD91B7FDB9F946" box="[380,521,1703,1728]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854">P. taeguensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244052322FDAE91B7FD30F946" author="Paik KY" box="[527,640,1703,1728]" pageId="16" pageNumber="2854" pagination="117 - 130" refId="ref7635" refString="Paik KY. 1992. Three new species of the genus Poecilochroa (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Korea. Korean Arachnol. 7: 117 - 130." type="journal article" year="1992">Paik, 1992</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
: epigyne with a median depression and large, bean-like spermathecae (compare 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244042323FD8E979EFD18FF21" author="Patel SK" box="[559,680,142,167]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="44 - 46" refId="ref7664" refString="Patel SK. 1988. A new species of spider of the genus: Sergiolus (Gnaphosidae) from India. Biol Bull India. 10: 44 - 46." type="journal article" year="1988">Patel 1988</bibRefCitation>
, fig 1c–d with 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244042323FCFA979EFBFCFF21" author="Chatzaki M &amp; Thaler K &amp; Mylonas M" box="[859,1100,142,167]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="559 - 601" refId="ref7044" refString="Chatzaki M, Thaler K, Mylonas M. 2002 a. Ground spiders (Gnaphosidae; Araneae) of Crete (Greece). Taxonomy and distribution. I. Rev Suisse Zool. 109: 559 - 601. doi: 10.5962 / bhl. part. 79611." type="journal article" year="2002">Chatzaki et al. 2002a</bibRefCitation>
, figs 10–11; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244042323FF5797A1FD99FF4C" author="Lissner J &amp; Chatzaki M" box="[246,553,177,202]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="16 - 21" refId="ref7550" refString="Lissner J, Chatzaki M. 2016. First records of Poecilochroa taborensis Levy, 1999 (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Greece and Cyprus with notes on some closely related species. Nieuwsbrief SPINED. 36: 16 - 21." type="journal article" year="2016">Lissner and Chatzaki 2016</bibRefCitation>
, fig. 4A–D; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244042323FD1897A1FC9AFF4C" author="Paik KY" box="[697,810,177,202]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="117 - 130" refId="ref7635" refString="Paik KY. 1992. Three new species of the genus Poecilochroa (Araneae: Gnaphosidae) from Korea. Korean Arachnol. 7: 117 - 130." type="journal article" year="1992">Paik 1992</bibRefCitation>
, figs 26–27). Based on these observations, we propose to transfer 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044042323FDE597C4FD7BFF6B" authorityName="Patel" authorityYear="1988" box="[580,715,212,237]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiarae">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144042323FDE597C4FD7BFF6B" box="[580,715,212,237]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">S. khodiarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044042323FD5097C4FCCCFF6B" authorityName="Westring" authorityYear="1874" box="[753,892,212,237]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144042323FD5097C4FCCCFF6B" box="[753,892,212,237]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">Poecilochroa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF236D344042323FF6197E6FEC5FE89" blockId="17.[160,1155,142,271]" box="[192,373,246,271]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144042323FF6197E6FF45FE89" box="[192,245,246,271]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">Male</emphasis>
. Unknown.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF236D344042323FF01965BFE3DFEE3" blockId="17.[160,1155,331,461]" box="[160,397,331,357]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144042323FF01965BFE3DFEE3" bold="true" box="[160,397,331,357]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">Nomenclatural note</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF236D344042323FF01967EFC52FE4B" blockId="17.[160,1155,331,461]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">
Since the specific epithet of this species is based on the name of the 
<typeStatus id="54F6887144042323FC12967EFC55FE01" box="[947,997,366,391]" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">type</typeStatus>
locality (
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B2244042323FBEB967EFF67FE2C" author="Patel SK" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" pagination="44 - 46" refId="ref7664" refString="Patel SK. 1988. A new species of spider of the genus: Sergiolus (Gnaphosidae) from India. Biol Bull India. 10: 44 - 46." type="journal article" year="1988">Patel 1988</bibRefCitation>
), the name is therefore proposed to be modified as 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044042323FCBB9681FCDDFE2C" authorityName="Sankaran &amp; Caleb &amp; Sebastian" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Patel" baseAuthorityYear="1988" box="[794,877,401,426]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Poecilochroa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiar">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144042323FCBB9681FCDDFE2C" box="[794,877,401,426]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">khodiar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(considering it a noun in apposition), instead of 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D5044042323FE0296A4FDA0FE4B" authorityName="Patel" authorityYear="1988" box="[419,528,436,461]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Sergiolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="khodiarae">
<emphasis id="B939EAC144042323FE0296A4FDA0FE4B" box="[419,528,436,461]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="2855">khodiarae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as mentioned in the original description.
</paragraph>
